            "description": "Retrieves a single tour by its unique ID.\n\n## Endpoint\n`GET {{URL}}api/v1/tours/:id`\n\n## Path Parameters\n| Parameter | Type   | Required | Description          |\n|-----------|--------|----------|----------------------|\n| id        | string | Yes      | The unique ID of the tour to retrieve |\n\n## Authentication\nRequires a valid JWT bearer token passed via the `Authorization` header:\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer {{jwt}}\n```\n\n## Responses\n| Status | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| 200 OK | Successfully retrieved the tour object |\n| 401 Unauthorized | Missing or invalid JWT token |\n| 404 Not Found | No tour found with the given ID |"
