            "description": "## Get Monthly Plan\n\nRetrieves the monthly plan for tours for a specific year. The response includes a breakdown of tours scheduled for each month, providing details such as the number of tours, tour names, and the month they are planned for.\n\n**Method:** `GET`\n\n**Endpoint:** `{{URL}}api/v1/tours/monthly-plan/2021`\n\n### Path Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type   | Description                              |\n|-----------|--------|------------------------------------------|\n| `year`    | Number | The year for which to retrieve the monthly tour plan (e.g., `2021`) |\n\n### Authentication\n\nThis request requires a valid JWT token. Set the `jwt` variable in your active environment before sending.\n\n### Example Response\n\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"plan\": [\n      {\n        \"numTourStarts\": 3,\n        \"tours\": [\"The Forest Hiker\", \"The Sea Explorer\", \"The Snow Adventurer\"],\n        \"month\": 1\n      },\n      {\n        \"numTourStarts\": 1,\n        \"tours\": [\"The City Wanderer\"],\n        \"month\": 2\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Notes\n\n- The year is passed as a path parameter in the URL.\n- Returns one entry per month that has at least one tour scheduled.\n- Months with no tours are not included in the response."
