            "description": "## Get Tour Stats\n\nRetrieves aggregated statistical data about all tours in the system. This endpoint uses a database aggregation pipeline to compute meaningful metrics grouped by tour difficulty.\n\n### Response Data\n\nThe response typically includes statistics such as:\n\n- **Number of tours** per difficulty level (e.g., easy, medium, difficult)\n- **Average, minimum, and maximum ratings** across tours\n- **Average, minimum, and maximum prices** per difficulty group\n- **Total number of ratings** submitted\n\n### Example Use Cases\n\n- Display a summary dashboard of tour offerings\n- Compare pricing and quality across difficulty levels\n- Provide users with an overview before browsing individual tours\n\n### Authentication\n\nThis endpoint may require a valid JWT token depending on the server configuration. If authentication is required, include the token in the `Authorization` header:\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer {{jwt}}\n```\n\n### Method & URL\n\n```\nGET {{URL}}api/v1/tours/tour-stats\n```\n\n### Response Example\n\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"stats\": [\n      {\n        \"difficulty\": \"easy\",\n        \"numTours\": 3,\n        \"numRatings\": 27,\n        \"avgRating\": 4.7,\n        \"avgPrice\": 1270,\n        \"minPrice\": 397,\n        \"maxPrice\": 1997\n      },\n      {\n        \"difficulty\": \"difficult\",\n        \"numTours\": 2,\n        \"numRatings\": 41,\n        \"avgRating\": 4.6,\n        \"avgPrice\": 1750,\n        \"minPrice\": 997,\n        \"maxPrice\": 2997\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```"
