            "description": "## Get All Reviews on Tour\n\nRetrieves all reviews associated with a specific tour, identified by its tour ID in the URL path.\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET {{URL}}api/v1/tours/5c88fa8cf4afda39709c295d/reviews`\n\n**Tour ID:** `5c88fa8cf4afda39709c295d`\n\n### Authentication\n\nThis request requires a Bearer token for authentication. The token is sourced from the `{{jwt}}` variable (set in the active environment).\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer {{jwt}}\n```\n\n### Response\n\nOn success, the endpoint returns a list of reviews for the specified tour. Each review typically includes details such as the review text, rating, and the user who submitted it.\n\n**Example response shape:**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"results\": 2,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"reviews\": [\n      {\n        \"_id\": \"...\",\n        \"review\": \"Amazing tour!\",\n        \"rating\": 5,\n        \"tour\": \"5c88fa8cf4afda39709c295d\",\n        \"user\": { ... }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n| Status Code | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `200 OK` | Successfully retrieved the list of reviews |\n| `401 Unauthorized` | Missing or invalid Bearer token |\n| `404 Not Found` | Tour with the specified ID does not exist |"
